# C Unikernel for LLM Serving

This project implements a C unikernel for serving large language models with the following features:
- x86_64 QEMU target
- llama.cpp integration for model inference
- HTTP API for model interaction
- JSON-based configuration
- GPU acceleration (CUDA)
- vLLM-inspired optimizations

## Directories

- `src/` - Source code
- `include/` - Header files
- `docs/` - Documentation
- `tests/` - Test cases
- `build/` - Build artifacts